resources NO(24)
notes
SPEAR will be used to produce small-scale irregularities detectable by the 
CUTLASS radars in Finland and Iceland
The ESR 32m dish will be scanned 180 degrees in azimuth at fixed elevation to 
investigate the heater-modified plasma parameters and ion line spectra across 
the heated volume

